tnref6">[6]</a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal"> Ceci SJ Williams WM (2011) Reply to Drago: Culture and history are important in understanding the low number of women PNAS 108(21) E115. doi: 10.1073/pnas.1103900108 </span></h1><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span></p></body></html>